[SPEAKER_01] I to se da, osjetiti.

743
00:37:48,699 --> 00:37:51,420
[SPEAKER_01] Neka moja iskustva,

744
00:37:51,420 --> 00:37:53,900
[SPEAKER_01] dalo se osjetiti odluka i tako,

745
00:37:53,900 --> 00:37:55,880
[SPEAKER_01] a onda pogledaš sastav zapravo

746
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] vijeća ustavnog suda,

747
00:37:57,960 --> 00:37:59,760
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda imaš razloga

748
00:37:59,760 --> 00:38:01,039
[SPEAKER_01] pretpostaviti da je

749
00:38:01,039 --> 00:38:03,880
[SPEAKER_01] to vijeće se rukovodilo

750
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:05,980
[SPEAKER_01] i nekim...

751
00:38:05,980 --> 00:38:07,760
[SPEAKER_01] jer dio je iz HDZ-a došao,

752
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] dio je došao iz SDP-a

753
00:38:09,460 --> 00:38:10,519
[SPEAKER_01] i onda vidiš zapravo,

754
00:38:10,519 --> 00:38:13,260
[SPEAKER_01] moguće je da su tu neki ali...

755
00:38:13,260 --> 00:38:13,639
[SPEAKER_00] Tako.

756
00:38:13,639 --> 00:38:16,380
[SPEAKER_00] Što želite reći da možda da se događa

757
00:38:16,380 --> 00:38:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] da se kod nas izaberu sudci

758
00:38:18,579 --> 00:38:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji možda nisu ono A1,

759
00:38:21,340 --> 00:38:23,519
[SPEAKER_00] ali zato odgovaraju objema stranama?

760
00:38:23,519 --> 00:38:26,940
[SPEAKER_01] Može se to zapravo dogoditi,

761
00:38:26,940 --> 00:38:28,940
[SPEAKER_01] jer te strane po tim kriterijima

762
00:38:28,940 --> 00:38:30,019
[SPEAKER_01] u konačnici odlučuju.

763
00:38:30,019 --> 00:38:33,860
[SPEAKER_00] Simpatičniji su za obje strane,

764
00:38:33,860 --> 00:38:35,719
[SPEAKER_00] a to što su možda...

765
00:38:35,719 --> 00:38:37,400
[SPEAKER_00] kvalitetom manje?

766
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:38,579
[SPEAKER_01] Čujte, nažalost,

767
00:38:38,579 --> 00:38:40,920
[SPEAKER_01] mi moramo razgovarati na taj način.

768
00:38:40,920 --> 00:38:43,960
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to čovjek s karaterom,

769
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:45,800
[SPEAKER_01] je li naš čovjek ili to nije naš čovjek?

770
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:47,699
[SPEAKER_01] Na što bi trebalo najprije gledati,

771
00:38:47,699 --> 00:38:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] gospodine Čmanja?

772
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:49,280
[SPEAKER_01] Čujte, ono na što zapravo

773
00:38:49,280 --> 00:38:50,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ustav kaže,

774
00:38:50,659 --> 00:38:53,380
[SPEAKER_01] koji su zapravo iskusni,

775
00:38:53,380 --> 00:38:55,840
[SPEAKER_01] diplomirani pravnici

776
00:38:55,840 --> 00:38:57,840
[SPEAKER_01] i zapravo koji su dokazani

777
00:38:57,840 --> 00:38:59,260
[SPEAKER_01] u tom smijesu svojim stručnim,

778
00:38:59,260 --> 00:39:00,659
[SPEAKER_01] znanstvenim radom

779
00:39:00,659 --> 00:39:02,159
[SPEAKER_01] i nekim svojim javnim djelovajima.

780
00:39:02,159 --> 00:39:03,900
[SPEAKER_01] To bi bio kriterij.

781
00:39:03,900 --> 00:39:05,699
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno da tu mogu biti

782
00:39:05,699 --> 00:39:11,519
[SPEAKER_01] i profesori na pravnim fakultetima.

783
00:39:11,519 --> 00:39:14,239
[SPEAKER_01] Oni jedino mogu zapravo,

784
00:39:14,239 --> 00:39:16,599
[SPEAKER_01] i vjerojatno je to pretežito

785
00:39:16,599 --> 00:39:17,360
[SPEAKER_01] u njihovom slučaju,

786
00:39:17,360 --> 00:39:18,340
[SPEAKER_01] da oni mogu poniviti

787
00:39:18,340 --> 00:39:20,900
[SPEAKER_01] znanstvene radove koje su servirali javnosti,

788
00:39:21,119 --> 00:39:24,400
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda je javnost ona koja je zainteresirana

789
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:25,480
[SPEAKER_01] mogla zaključiti

790
00:39:25,480 --> 00:39:30,300
[SPEAKER_01] da li je taj znanstveni rad doista ozbiljan,

791
00:39:30,300 --> 00:39:32,679
[SPEAKER_01] izaziva pozor u stručnom smislu

792
00:39:32,679 --> 00:39:33,780
[SPEAKER_01] ili nije.

793
00:39:33,780 --> 00:39:35,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam,

794
00:39:35,480 --> 00:39:37,800
[SPEAKER_01] velika masa ovih prijavljenih

795
00:39:37,800 --> 00:39:39,840
[SPEAKER_01] hoće li moći u tom smislu

796
00:39:39,840 --> 00:39:41,320
[SPEAKER_01] nešto konkretno ponuditi.

797
00:39:41,320 --> 00:39:44,260
[SPEAKER_01] Da bi zapravo zadovolili

798
00:39:44,260 --> 00:39:47,260
[SPEAKER_01] taj kriterij da su oni istaknuti

799
00:39:47,260 --> 00:39:50,179
[SPEAKER_01] diplomirani pravnici

800
00:39:50,179 --> 00:39:53,300
[SPEAKER_01] koji su se u svom do sadašnjem radu

801
00:39:53,300 --> 00:39:56,280
[SPEAKER_01] dokazali sa svojim stručnim

802
00:39:56,280 --> 00:39:57,519
[SPEAKER_01] znanstvenim radovima

803
00:39:57,519 --> 00:39:59,260
[SPEAKER_01] i javnim djelovanjem.

804
00:39:59,260 --> 00:40:01,679
[SPEAKER_00] I naravno da nemaju mrlju na karijeri.

805
00:40:01,679 --> 00:40:04,360
[SPEAKER_01] I da nemaju zapravo neke mrlje na karijeri,

806
00:40:04,360 --> 00:40:06,400
[SPEAKER_01] da nemaju nekih tu zapravo

807
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:07,880
[SPEAKER_01] sigurnosnih zapreka

808
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:10,099
[SPEAKER_01] koje su na primjer

809
00:40:10,099 --> 00:40:11,420
[SPEAKER_01] po meni bile prisutne

810
00:40:11,420 --> 00:40:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] u slučaju gospodina Turudića.

811
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:17,239
[SPEAKER_00] I to je otprilike to.

812
00:40:17,239 --> 00:40:19,239
[SPEAKER_00] Predsjednik Milanović

813
00:40:19,239 --> 00:40:21,059
[SPEAKER_00] je dosta kritizirao

814
00:40:21,059 --> 00:40:22,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ustavni sud, odnosno suce.

815
00:40:22,780 --> 00:40:26,099
[SPEAKER_00] Je li imao pravo po vama?

816
00:40:26,099 --> 00:40:30,260
[SPEAKER_01] Pa želite,

817
00:40:30,260 --> 00:40:33,280
[SPEAKER_01] meni naš predsjednik Milanović

818
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:33,980
[SPEAKER_01] imponira

819
00:40:33,980 --> 00:40:37,280
[SPEAKER_01] jer on ima jednu otresitost

820
00:40:37,280 --> 00:40:40,480
[SPEAKER_01] o svom nastupu.

821
00:40:40,480 --> 00:40:45,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ponekad je on doista i neodmiren čovjek

822
00:40:45,099 --> 00:40:47,840
[SPEAKER_01] u nekim svojim ocjenama ili procjenama,

823
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja sam primitivac iz Dalmacije,

824
00:40:49,539 --> 00:40:51,260
[SPEAKER_01] meni takav vokabular odgovara.

825
00:40:51,260 --> 00:40:54,500
[SPEAKER_01] Meni takav vokabular odgovara.

826
00:40:55,599 --> 00:40:56,860
[SPEAKER_01] gospodin Plenković je jedan

827
00:40:56,860 --> 00:40:58,599
[SPEAKER_01] i vrlo obrazovan čovjek.

828
00:40:58,599 --> 00:41:05,599
[SPEAKER_01] Njegova priča i objašnjenje ima svoju strukturu,

829
00:41:05,599 --> 00:41:08,420
