830
00:41:08,420 --> 00:41:10,699
[SPEAKER_01] ali je prilično sivo i bezlično.

831
00:41:11,079 --> 00:41:11,860
[SPEAKER_01] Znate, onako.

832
00:41:11,860 --> 00:41:14,079
[SPEAKER_01] Što bi se reklo bilistijevski.

833
00:41:14,079 --> 00:41:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] Volim jedan tako element divine u nastupu.

834
00:41:22,159 --> 00:41:24,219
[SPEAKER_01] Posebno mi imponiram Milanović

835
00:41:24,219 --> 00:41:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] kada je zapravo otresit i vrlo jasan

836
00:41:26,539 --> 00:41:27,900
[SPEAKER_01] prema Evropskoj uniji

837
00:41:27,900 --> 00:41:31,739
