838
00:41:31,739 --> 00:41:33,079
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da je to dobro

839
00:41:33,079 --> 00:41:34,760
[SPEAKER_01] da se jednostavno neke stvari ogole,

840
00:41:34,760 --> 00:41:37,119
[SPEAKER_01] da se učine bjelodanim

841
00:41:37,119 --> 00:41:38,780
[SPEAKER_01] kako bi javnost mogla suditi.

842
00:41:41,079 --> 00:41:44,460
[SPEAKER_01] Željeli smo i postali smo členovi Evropske unije,

843
00:41:44,460 --> 00:41:49,360
