[SPEAKER_01] zapravo nema karaktera apostolske istine.

845
00:41:51,659 --> 00:41:54,739
[SPEAKER_01] Mi moramo voditi računaj

846
00:41:54,739 --> 00:41:56,119
[SPEAKER_01] o nekom našem dostojanstvu.

847
00:41:56,119 --> 00:41:58,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam neki pretjerani domoljub,

848
00:41:58,420 --> 00:41:59,920
[SPEAKER_01] ali što sam stariji,

849
00:41:59,920 --> 00:42:00,900
