850
00:42:00,900 --> 00:42:02,840
[SPEAKER_01] do nacionalnog dostojanstva ove države.

851
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:06,679
[SPEAKER_01] A moramo zapravo štiti neki ustalni identitet.

852
00:42:06,679 --> 00:42:10,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ne možemo biti obične cikove

853
00:42:10,860 --> 00:42:12,739
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo nad čovječe ribice.

854
00:42:12,739 --> 00:42:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] Pa sve slijepo i bezuvjetno prihvatati

855
00:42:15,800 --> 00:42:16,739
