857
00:42:19,460 --> 00:42:23,400
[SPEAKER_00] Sad zapravo ste otvorili jednu zanimljivu temu.

858
00:42:23,400 --> 00:42:25,219
[SPEAKER_00] Prije, sad ću je opet reći,

859
00:42:25,219 --> 00:42:27,119
[SPEAKER_00] u onom sustavu se sudilo,

860
00:42:27,119 --> 00:42:28,780
