862
00:42:30,699 --> 00:42:32,239
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo su briselski,

863
00:42:32,239 --> 00:42:33,460
[SPEAKER_00] europski zakoni.

864
00:42:33,460 --> 00:42:35,659
[SPEAKER_00] Koji vam se čine

865
00:42:35,659 --> 00:42:37,159
