866
00:42:39,440 --> 00:42:40,619
[SPEAKER_01] Čujete zapravo,

867
00:42:40,619 --> 00:42:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] ja respektiram našu domicilnu,

868
00:42:43,380 --> 00:42:45,559
[SPEAKER_01] nacionalnu pamet.

869
00:42:45,559 --> 00:42:46,880
[SPEAKER_01] Razumijete me?

870
00:42:46,880 --> 00:42:50,019
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da to ima mudrih i pametnih ljudi.

871
00:42:52,900 --> 00:42:55,920
