884
00:43:25,639 --> 00:43:26,400
[SPEAKER_01] Evropske unije.

885
00:43:26,400 --> 00:43:28,780
[SPEAKER_01] I danas, sutra,

886
00:43:28,780 --> 00:43:30,039
