888
00:43:33,139 --> 00:43:34,500
[SPEAKER_01] napustiti Evropsku uniju

889
00:43:34,500 --> 00:43:35,260
[SPEAKER_01] upravo zbog toga.

890
00:43:35,260 --> 00:43:40,500
