896
00:43:50,300 --> 00:43:51,539
[SPEAKER_01] u isključivoj nadležnosti

897
00:43:51,539 --> 00:43:52,440
[SPEAKER_01] Republike Hrvatske

898
00:43:52,440 --> 00:43:54,280
[SPEAKER_01] kao članice Evropske unije.

899
00:43:54,280 --> 00:43:57,260
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo, zaključenje

900
00:43:57,260 --> 00:43:58,340
[SPEAKER_01] međunarodnih ugovora.

901
00:43:58,340 --> 00:43:59,940
[SPEAKER_01] Isto tako ja mislim

902
00:43:59,940 --> 00:44:01,280
[SPEAKER_01] u isključivoj nadležnosti

903
00:44:01,280 --> 00:44:03,639
[SPEAKER_01] Evropske unije

904
